## Overview

When designing a workshop and considering the manner of delivery it can be helpful to think about how information In this session we will spend some time thinking about how people learn new skills and the stages that you go through as you progress from a beginner to an expert.  

## The stages of learning

We can think of the learning process as a journey through a number of stages. One such model of this process is the Dreyfus model of skill acquisition. 

![Dreyfus model](fig/skill-level.png)
